    <physdesc id="aspace_ad5ee996ba90fa3742db29a8641dc176">Legal documents.</physdesc>
    <abstract id="aspace_9aa4f348b6c9f8f41aae4538c5f35187">Papers collected by Alan K. McAdams about the U.S. vs. IBM anti-trust case include a reasonably complete transcript of the trial; an additional copy of the transcript of McAdams' own testimony; exhibits used with McAdams' testimony; working papers and drafts used for the exhibits; depositions of other economists who appeared; other documents; and some personal files of Alan K. McAdams.</abstract>
